A duck walks into a bar. Goes up to the bartender and says, "Got any beans?" 

The bartender replies, "No, and we don't serve ducks in this bar". 

The duck leaves. Duck comes back to the bar the next day and says, "Got any beans?" 

The bartender says, "No, and I told you yesterday to get out". 

The duck leaves. Duck comes back the next day and asks, "Got any beans?" 

The bartender yells at the duck, "Get out! and if I see you come back tomorrow, I'll nail your foot to the floor!" 

The duck leaves. Duck comes back the next day and says, "Got any nails?" 

The bartender says, "No". 

Duck says, "Got any beans?"